Dragons' Den Ireland - Series 7, Episode 5




Dragons' Den returns for a seventh series featuring two new Deagons, Alison Cowzer and Eleanor McEvoy, alongside returning favourites Gavin Duffy, Barry O'Sullivan and Eamonn Quinn. The seventh series of Dragons' Den has also seen the highest percentage of female entrepreneurs in the history of the show.
